Package ru.nsu.lavitskaya.primenums

Interface PrimeChecker

All Known Implementing Classes:
ParallelStreamPrimeChecker, ParallelThreadsPrimeChecker, SequentialPrimeChecker
public interface PrimeChecker
Interface for checking if an array contains non-prime numbers. Provides a method for implementing different prime-checking strategies and a default method for checking if a single number is prime.
